#Born in [[India]], '''Prakash Motwani''' is a [[Software]] Professional amongst the first to contribute his work on [[Macromedia Flash]].

== Meaning == 

'''Prakash''' means '''light''', just as '''[[lux]]''' in Latin does. The word is from the Indo-European Sanskrit language, '''prakasam''' and is a common name mostly among Hindus, with some usage among Jains, Sikhs and recently [[Indic]] Christians.

The name is encountered in variant forms in the [[Indian Union]], [[Nepal]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Sri Lanka]], [[Mauritius]], and other countries where [[Indic]] races (i.e., people of East Indian origin)  live.